Interface Expression

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Assignable, FunctionCall, IntegerValue, Sequence, Value
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayAccessImpl, ArrayAssignmentImpl, BinaryExpressionImpl, BooleanValue, CoupleImpl, FieldAccessImpl, FieldAssignmentImpl, FunctionCallImpl, IntegerValueImpl, PointerAccessImpl, PointerAssignmentImpl, SequenceImpl, TypeConversionImpl, UnaryExpressionImpl, VariableAssignmentImpl, VariableUseImpl

    public interface Expression
    Represents an Expression node in the Abstract Syntax Tree node for the Bloc language. Declares the various semantics attributes for the node.
